{
  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline, prominently featuring two bridges illuminated with lights. The foreground showcases a modern, sleek bridge with evenly spaced, bright white lights stretching across the dark water. Behind it, a more traditional suspension bridge is visible, adorned with golden lights. In the distance, the city skyline rises dramatically, punctuated by tall buildings and a vibrant display of fireworks bursting in the air. The fireworks create a colorful spectacle with shades of red, white, and gold. The city lights contribute a mix of warm and cool tones, creating a dynamic contrast against the dark sky and water. The overall composition emphasizes the urban landscape and the celebratory atmosphere.",
